<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٨٤٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6916">‌يَحْيَى بْنُ خَلَفٍ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> نَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3160">‌عَبْدُ الْأَعْلَى </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> نَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6690">‌هِشَامٌ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1389">‌الْحَسَنِ، </a>أَنَّهُ كَانَ يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">«إِمَاطَةُ الْأَذَى حَلْقُ الرَّأْسِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>